Summary: The website offers Amazon Partner specialists who can answer questions and discuss how they can help an organization. If someone is looking to become a partner or needs technical, compliance, or billing support, they can fill out a form on the website to receive assistance. The website also offers additional resources such as AWS Partner Support, which is a global community of partners that leverages programs, expertise, and resources to build, market, and sell customer offerings. There is also support available related to AWS compliance, service-related technical issues, and account and billing-related inquiries. Finally, the website offers resources for learning about AWS and developing on AWS.
